n    <div class=\"tcs-review-grid\">\n\n      <!-- LEFT COLUMN: PROS, BONUS, WAGERING, GAMES -->\n      <div>\n\n        <!-- PROS & CONS -->\n        <div class=\"tcs-review-block\">\n          <span class=\"tcs-label-pill\">Snapshot \u2022 Pros &amp; Cons</span>\n          <h2>Is Legiano Casino Worth Your Deposit?</h2>\n          <p>\n            Legiano is designed for slot-heavy players who want a polished interface, a clear welcome package\n            and broad international coverage. With a 100% up to &euro;500 + 200 free spins bonus, multi-currency banking\n            and a wide GEO footprint across Europe, LATAM, Africa, India and emerging markets, it aims to be a \n            flexible choice for regular real-money casino play.\n          </p>\n          <div style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns:minmax(0,1fr) minmax(0,1fr); gap:20px; margin-top:10px;\">\n            <div>\n              <h3>Pros</h3>\n              <ul>\n                <li>Solid welcome offer: 100% up to &euro;500 plus 200 free spins for new players.</li>\n                <li>Modern UI that works well on both desktop and mobile devices.</li>\n                <li>Good game selection from well-known studios, with a strong emphasis on slots.</li>\n                <li>Available across Europe, LATAM, Africa, India and several emerging markets.</li>\n                <li>Multi-currency banking and a wide range of local payment methods.</li>\n              </ul>\n            </div>\n            <div>\n              <h3>Cons</h3>\n              <ul>\n                <li>Bonus terms, currencies and eligible games vary significantly by region.</li>\n                <li>Slots-focused welcome package may not appeal to table-game-only players.</li>\n                <li>Some payment options and providers are restricted in specific countries.</li>\n              </ul>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- WELCOME BONUS BREAKDOWN -->\n        <div class=\"tcs-review-block\">\n          <span class=\"tcs-label-pill\">Bonuses</span>\n          <h2>Legiano Welcome Bonus Breakdown</h2>\n          <p>\n            The Legiano welcome offer is built around a straightforward but appealing combination of matched funds\n            and free spins. Instead of a complex multi-stage ladder, it focuses on one strong entry package aimed\n            at players who want to start with a healthy slot bankroll:\n          </p>\n          <ul>\n            <li><strong>Total bonus value:</strong> 100% match up to &euro;500 on your first deposit.</li>\n            <li><strong>Extra value:</strong> 200 free spins on selected slot games.</li>\n            <li><strong>Audience:</strong> primarily slot fans who like to spread their play across several days.</li>\n          </ul>\n          <p>\n            This structure gives you a clean, easy-to-understand bonus: deposit once, double your balance up to &euro;500\n            and unlock 200 free spins to extend your play time. It\u2019s particularly attractive if you prefer testing a new\n            lobby with a mixture of balance play and spin-based value rather than chasing a massive headline number.\n          </p>\n          <p class=\"tcs-tagline\">\n            Exact currency caps, spin allocations and bonus codes can change by country or campaign, so always check\n            the latest Legiano promotions page from your location before depositing.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- WAGERING REQUIREMENTS -->\n        <div class=\"tcs-review-block\">\n          <span class=\"tcs-label-pill\">Bonus Rules</span>\n          <h2>Wagering Requirements &amp; Important Terms</h2>\n          <p>\n            As with any sizable <strong>real-money casino bonus</strong>, Legiano attaches wagering conditions and\n            a few important restrictions. While exact figures vary over time, you should be prepared for rules such as:\n          </p>\n          <ul>\n            <li>A minimum qualifying deposit to activate the 100% match and free spins bundle.</li>\n            <li>Standard wagering requirements on bonus funds and potentially on free spin winnings.</li>\n            <li>Slots contributing 100% to wagering, with table games and live casino contributing less or being excluded.</li>\n            <li>Maximum bet caps while your bonus is active to prevent high-risk betting patterns.</li>\n          </ul>\n          <p>\n            Because Legiano is active in multiple regions, wagering time limits, game-eligibility lists and restricted\n            payment methods can differ by jurisdiction. If you are new to bonuses, consider starting with a smaller deposit\n            to get a feel for how quickly wagering progresses before committing to the full &euro;500 match.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- GAMES & SOFTWARE -->\n        <div class=\"tcs-review-block\">\n          <span class=\"tcs-label-pill\">Games &amp; Providers</span>\n          <h2>Game Selection &amp; Software Providers</h2>\n          <p>\n            Legiano\u2019s lobby leans strongly toward slots but still maintains a balanced spread of table games and live dealer\n            titles. A typical experience includes:\n          </p>\n          <ul>\n            <li>\n              <strong>Video slots and jackpots</strong> from a mix of established and mid-tier studios, covering classic \n              3-reel games, modern feature-heavy slots and progressive titles.\n            </li>\n            <li>\n              <strong>Table games</strong> such as blackjack, roulette and baccarat in both RNG and live formats.\n            </li>\n            <li>\n              <strong>Live casino rooms</strong> hosted by human dealers, including popular game-show style titles.\n            </li>\n            <li>\n              A selection of <strong>instant-win and speciality games</strong> for quick sessions between longer slot runs.\n            </li>\n          </ul>\n   