t method.</li>\n            <li>Account limits, self-exclusion tools and other responsible gambling options.</li>\n          </ul>\n          <p>\n            If you ever feel that gambling is impacting your finances or wellbeing, you should use Legiano\u2019s limit tools,\n            take breaks and contact independent support organisations in your region. No bonus or promotion is worth\n            playing beyond what you can comfortably afford.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- VERDICT -->\n        <div class=\"tcs-review-block tcs-verdict-box\">\n          <span class=\"tcs-label-pill\">TopCasinoScout Verdict</span>\n          <h2>Should You Play at Legiano Casino?</h2>\n          <p class=\"tcs-verdict-highlight\">\n            With a TCS score of 8,700, Legiano earns our #6 spot globally thanks to its solid &euro;500 + 200 free spins\n            welcome bonus, modern interface and strong availability across Europe, LATAM, Africa, India and key emerging markets.\n          </p>\n          <p>\n            It\u2019s a strong option for slot-focused players who value a clean design, familiar local payment methods and a\n            single welcome package that\u2019s easy to understand. The combination of matched funds and 200 free spins gives you\n            enough runway to properly test the lobby and find your favourite games.\n          </p>\n          <p>\n            If you are looking for ultra-high headline bonuses or ultra-local casinos focused on just one market, you may\n            want to compare Legiano with other brands in our rankings. But as an all-rounder with wide coverage and a fair\n            <strong>casino deposit bonus</strong>, it comfortably earns its place in the upper tier of our list.\n          </p>\n\n          <div class=\"tcs-hero-ctas\" style=\"margin-top:14px;\">\n            <a class=\"tcs-btn-primary\"\n               href=\"#\"\n               target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n              Go to Legiano &amp; Claim Bonus\n            </a>\n            <a class=\"tcs-btn-secondary\"\n               href=\"/top-casino-bonuses\"\n               target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n              Compare More Casino Bonuses\n            </a>\n          </div>\n\n          <div class=\"tcs-internal-links\">\n            Looking for alternatives? Check our\n            <a href=\"/casino-rankings\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n              global casino rankings\n            </a>,\n            explore\n            <a href=\"/no-deposit-bonuses\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n              no-deposit casino bonuses\n            </a>,\n            or see country-specific deals on\n            <a href=\"/top-casino-bonuses\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n              our bonus comparison page\n            </a>.\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</section>";
